Package com.irurueta.navigation.inertial.navigators

Class NEDInertialNavigator

java.lang.Object
com.irurueta.navigation.inertial.navigators.NEDInertialNavigator
public class NEDInertialNavigator extends Object
Runs precision local-navigation-frame inertial navigation equations. NOTE: only the attitude update and specific force frame transformation phases are precise). This implementation is based on the equations defined in "Principles of GNSS, Inertial, and Multisensor Integrated Navigation Systems, Second Edition" and on the companion software available at: https://github.com/ymjdz/MATLAB-Codes/blob/master/Nav_equations_NED.m

    • navigate

      public void navigate(double timeInterval, double oldLatitude, double oldLongitude, double oldHeight, com.irurueta.navigation.frames.CoordinateTransformation oldC, double oldVn, double oldVe, double oldVd, double fx, double fy, double fz, double angularRateX, double angularRateY, double angularRateZ, double accuracyThreshold, com.irurueta.navigation.frames.NEDFrame result) throws InertialNavigatorException, com.irurueta.navigation.frames.InvalidSourceAndDestinationFrameTypeException
      Runs precision local-navigation-frame inertial navigation equations. NOTE: only the attitude update and specific force frame transformation phases are precise.
      Parameters:
      timeInterval - time interval between epochs expressed in seconds (s).
      oldLatitude - previous latitude expressed in radians (rad).
      oldLongitude - previous longitude expressed in radians (rad).
      oldHeight - previous height expressed in meters (m).
      oldC - previous body-to-NED coordinate transformation.
      oldVn - previous velocity north-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along NED-frame axes and expressed in meters per second (m/s).
      oldVe - previous velocity east-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along NED-frame axes and expressed in meters per second (m/s).
      oldVd - previous velocity down-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along NED-frame axes and expressed in meters per second (m/s).
      fx - specific force x-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in meters per squared second (m/s^2).
      fy - specific force y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in meters per squared second (m/s^2).
      fz - specific force z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in meters per squared second (m/s^2).
      angularRateX - angular rate x-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      angularRateY - angular rate y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      angularRateZ - angular rate z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      accuracyThreshold - threshold to determine whether a matrix is a valid rotation or not.
      result - instance where new estimated NED frame containing new body position, velocity and coordinate transformation matrix will be stored.
      Throws:
      InertialNavigatorException - if navigation fails due to numerical instabilities.
      com.irurueta.navigation.frames.InvalidSourceAndDestinationFrameTypeException - if source or destination frame types of previous body-to-NED-frame coordinate transformation matrix are invalid.

      fx - specific force x-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in meters per squared second (m/s^2).
      fy - specific force y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in meters per squared second (m/s^2).
      fz - specific force z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in meters per squared second (m/s^2).
      angularRateX - angular rate x-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      angularRateY - angular rate y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      angularRateZ - angular rate z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      result - instance where new estimated NED frame containing new body position, velocity and coordinate transformation matrix will be stored.
      Throws:
      InertialNavigatorException - if navigation fails due to numerical instabilities.
      com.irurueta.navigation.frames.InvalidSourceAndDestinationFrameTypeException - if source or destination frame types of previous body-to-NED-frame coordinate transformation matrix are invalid.

      oldLatitude - previous latitude expressed in radians (rad).
      oldLongitude - previous longitude expressed in radians (rad).
      oldHeight - previous height expressed in meters (m).
      oldC - previous body-to-NED coordinate transformation.
      oldVelocity - previous velocity of body frame with respect ECEF frame resolved along north, east and down axes.

      fy - specific force y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval.

      angularRateY - angular rate y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      angularRateZ - angular rate z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      result - instance where new estimated NED frame containing new body position, velocity and coordinate transformation matrix will be stored.

      Runs precision local-navigation-frame inertial navigation equations. NOTE: only the attitude update and specific force frame transformation phases are precise.

      fz - specific force z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in meters per squared second (m/s^2).

      angularRateZ - angular rate z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval.

      oldLongitude - previous longitude angle.
      oldHeight - previous height.
      oldC - previous body-to-NED coordinate transformation.
      oldSpeedN - previous velocity north-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along NED-frame axes.
      oldSpeedE - previous velocity east-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along NED-frame axes.
      oldSpeedD - previous velocity down-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along NED-frame axes.
      kinematics - body kinematics containing specific forces and angular rates applied to the body.
      result - instance where new estimated NED frame containing new body position, velocity and coordinate transformation matrix will be stored.
      Throws:
      InertialNavigatorException - if navigation fails due to numerical instabilities.
      com.irurueta.navigation.frames.InvalidSourceAndDestinationFrameTypeException - if source or destination frame types of previous body-to-NED-frame coordinate transformation matrix are invalid.

      Runs precision local-navigation-frame inertial navigation equations. NOTE: only the attitude update and specific force frame transformation phases are precise.
      Parameters:
      timeInterval - time interval between epochs expressed in seconds (s).
      oldFrame - previous NED frame containing body position, velocity and coordinate transformation matrix.
      fx - specific force x-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in meters per squared second (m/s^2).
      fy - specific force y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in meters per squared second (m/s^2).

      angularRateZ - angular rate z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval.
      accuracyThreshold - threshold to determine whether a matrix is a valid rotation or not.
      result - instance where new estimated NED frame containing new body position, velocity and coordinate transformation matrix will be stored.
      Throws:
      InertialNavigatorException - if navigation fails due to numerical instabilities.

      angularRateZ - angular rate z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).

      Runs precision local-navigation-frame inertial navigation equations. NOTE: only the attitude update and specific force frame transformation phases are precise.

      Runs precision local-navigation-frame inertial navigation equations. NOTE: only the attitude update and specific force frame transformation phases are precise.

      oldPosition - previous curvilinear position expressed in terms of latitude, longitude and height.

      angularRateY - angular rate y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      angularRateZ - angular rate z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).

      fx - specific force x-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval.

      angularRateY - angular rate y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      angularRateZ - angular rate z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).

      public com.irurueta.navigation.frames.NEDFrame navigateAndReturnNew(double timeInterval, com.irurueta.navigation.frames.NEDFrame oldFrame, double fx, double fy, double fz, double angularRateX, double angularRateY, double angularRateZ, double accuracyThreshold) throws InertialNavigatorException
      Runs precision local-navigation-frame inertial navigation equations. NOTE: only the attitude update and specific force frame transformation phases are precise.
      Parameters:
      timeInterval - time interval between epochs expressed in seconds (s).
      oldFrame - previous NED frame containing body position, velocity and coordinate transformation matrix.
      fx - specific force x-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in meters per squared second (m/s^2).
      fy - specific force y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in meters per squared second (m/s^2).
      fz - specific force z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in meters per squared second (m/s^2).
      angularRateX - angular rate x-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      angularRateY - angular rate y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      angularRateZ - angular rate z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      accuracyThreshold - threshold to determine whether a matrix is a valid rotation or not.
      Returns:
      estimated NED frame containing new body position, velocity and coordinate transformation matrix.
      Throws:
      InertialNavigatorException - if navigation fails due to numerical instabilities.

      fy - specific force y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in meters per squared second (m/s^2).
      fz - specific force z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in meters per squared second (m/s^2).
      angularRateX - angular rate x-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval.
      angularRateY - angular rate y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval.
      angularRateZ - angular rate z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval.
      accuracyThreshold - threshold to determine whether a matrix is a valid rotation or not.
      Returns:
      estimated NED frame containing new body position, velocity and coordinate transformation matrix.
      Throws:
      InertialNavigatorException - if navigation fails due to numerical instabilities.

      angularRateX - angular rate x-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      angularRateY - angular rate y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      angularRateZ - angular rate z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      accuracyThreshold - threshold to determine whether a matrix is a valid rotation or not.
      result - instance where new estimated NED frame containing new body position, velocity and coordinate transformation matrix will be stored.
      Throws:
      InertialNavigatorException - if navigation fails due to numerical instabilities.
      com.irurueta.navigation.frames.InvalidSourceAndDestinationFrameTypeException - if source or destination frame types of previous body-to-NED-frame coordinate transformation matrix are invalid.

      result - instance where new estimated NED frame containing new body position, velocity and coordinate transformation matrix will be stored.

      InertialNavigatorException - if navigation fails due to numerical instabilities.

      Runs precision local-navigation-frame inertial navigation equations. NOTE: only the attitude update and specific force frame transformation phases are precise.
      Parameters:
      timeInterval - time interval between epochs expressed in seconds (s).
      oldPosition - previous curvilinear position expressed in terms of latitude, longitude and height.
      oldC - previous body-to-NED coordinate transformation.
      oldVn - previous velocity north-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along NED-frame axes and expressed in meters per second (m/s).
      oldVe - previous velocity east-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along NED-frame axes and expressed in meters per second (m/s).
      oldVd - previous velocity down-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along NED-frame axes and expressed in meters per second (m/s).
      fx - specific force x-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval.
      fy - specific force y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval.
      fz - specific force z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval.
      angularRateX - angular rate x-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval.
      angularRateY - angular rate y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval.
      angularRateZ - angular rate z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval.
      accuracyThreshold - threshold to determine whether a matrix is a valid rotation or not.
      result - instance where new estimated NED frame containing new body position, velocity and coordinate transformation matrix will be stored.

      InertialNavigatorException - if navigation fails due to numerical instabilities.

      fy - specific force y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval.
      fz - specific force z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval.
      angularRateX - angular rate x-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      angularRateY - angular rate y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      angularRateZ - angular rate z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      accuracyThreshold - threshold to determine whether a matrix is a valid rotation or not.
      result - instance where new estimated NED frame containing new body position, velocity and coordinate transformation matrix will be stored.
      Throws:
      InertialNavigatorException - if navigation fails due to numerical instabilities.

      angularRateX - angular rate x-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      angularRateY - angular rate y-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      angularRateZ - angular rate z-coordinate of body frame with respect ECEF frame, resolved along body-frame axes, averaged over time interval and expressed in radians per second (rad/s).
      accuracyThreshold - threshold to determine whether a matrix is a valid rotation or not.
      Returns:
      estimated NED frame containing new body position, velocity and coordinate transformation matrix.
      Throws:
      InertialNavigatorException - if navigation fails due to numerical instabilities.
